Program: Last Word
Title: 15/05/2009
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00k9pb4
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 17 May 2009
Matthew Bannister talks to Professor John Q Barrett and Whitney Harris about the life of Nuremburg war crimes prosecutor Henry T King; Richard Adams and Jason Goodwin about the life of New Age writer John Michell; Rodric Braithwaite on Soviet General Valentin Varennikov; Tony Bailey and Roger Mansfield discuss the father of British surfing, Bill Bailey. Show less